{"tid":2195352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【美國大選】特朗普民調追貼拜登 獲佛州拉美裔支持","createTime":"2020-09-09T06:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:51:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad0ca84d321a23368398d32ae036a985720403e","tid":2195352,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"距離11月3日的美國大選只有8周，總統特朗普和前副總統拜登的支持度叮噹馬頭。在6個關鍵搖擺州之一的佛羅里達州，特朗普和拜登均獲得28%支持度，特朗普較2016年獲更多拉美裔支持。馬瑞斯特學院民意研究所總監米林戈夫（Lee Miringoff）形容，情況不尋常，該州的民調多數不會追得如此貼。<br />\n<br />\n拜登（Joe Biden）過去幾個月6大搖擺州（賓夕法尼亞州、密歇根州、威斯康星州、佛羅里達州、北卡羅來納州和亞利桑那州）都處於領先位置，但特朗普在全國民調急起直追，拜登領先的優勢明顯收窄。<br />\n<br />\n美國全國廣播公司（NBC）與馬瑞斯特學院（Marist College）針對佛州的民調發現，兩人支持度分別是48%；在已登記選民中，特朗普以48%支持度，險勝拜登的47%。特朗普4年前以1.2個百分點險勝對手希拉里（Hillary Clinton），奪下佛州。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，拉丁美裔傳統上多數支持民主黨，但民調顯示，50%的人支持特朗普，高過拜登的46%。特朗普2016年時，僅取得35%拉美裔支持，希拉里的支持度多達62%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，不少4年前支持特朗普的高齡選民，轉為支持拜登。在2016年，57%高齡選民支持特朗普，遠多過希拉里40%；最新的民調顯示，49%的人支持拜登，高過特朗普的48%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2745000/2748071/202009_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2745000%2F2748071%2F202009_1024.png&h=67666536&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0502fcf062fb60472124349228b747134baba0cb","tid":2195352,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/digitalspyuk.cdnds.net/16/42/1477043578-trump-gif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fdigitalspyuk.cdnds.net%2F16%2F42%2F1477043578-trump-gif.gif&h=44fcb2fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ba5bc2786b95d81a0f0d5e93b6e681e38f66cc4","tid":2195352,"uid":274435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"拜主席訓係度選都贏<br />\n識講普通話有鬼妹屌既日子不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b686bbbbfff26de0b90b18211acace6a293485e5","tid":2195352,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"呢啲民調收皮啦<br />\n拜登一定贏啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f78e72ca6a44d84276c338e13df17939d73b98","tid":2195352,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:33:50.000Z","msg":"China Joe sure win<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d412742eed8ed18b3c48203b41f49336deeaf680","tid":2195352,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba5bc2786b95d81a0f0d5e93b6e681e38f66cc4","tid":2195352,"uid":274435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"拜主席訓係度選都贏<br />\n識講普通話有鬼妹屌既日子不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"幼幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f2391cef1d7da93ee0499f7a67b03218a052dd","tid":2195352,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"我唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜登一定贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拜登一定大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704ca416d27223759db293520b3739f6238db5e4","tid":2195352,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-